	<h1 class="title">一个互联网上走红的基本款品牌，可以给大公司什么借鉴？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/75588/small/75588.jpg?1431919455" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">张金晶 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-25 09:00:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15869/medium/15869.jpg?1444399602" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="15869" data-title="《一个互联网上走红的基本款品牌，可以给大公司什么借鉴？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/15869/medium/15869.jpg?1444399602" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/15869.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
